{"type":"message","id":"61b9528c","parentId":"6d92527b","timestamp":"2026-04-06T05:48:15.982Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A new session was started via /new or /reset. Run your Session Startup sequence - read the required files before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Monday, April 6th, 2026 — 1:48 PM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-06 05:48 UTC"}],"timestamp":1775454495975}}
{"type":"message","id":"eb62c37b","parentId":"61b9528c","timestamp":"2026-04-06T05:48:22.860Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user started a new session. According to my instructions, I need to run a Session Startup sequence - read the required files before responding. But wait, the system prompt already says \"Project Context\" files were injected, which means they've already been loaded. Let me check what I need to do:\n\n1. The instruction says \"read the required files before responding\" - but the context already shows files were loaded (AGENTS.md, SOUL.md, TOOLS.md, IDENTITY.md, USER.md, HEARTBEAT.md, MEMORY.md)\n\n2. Then greet the user in my configured persona, if one is provided\n\n3. From IDENTITY.md, there's no specific persona defined - it's just a template\n4. From SOUL.md, there's OpenClaw Soul which gives some tone guidance\n\n5. Keep it 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do\n6. If runtime model differs from default_model, mention the default model\n\nLooking at the runtime info:\n- model=codingplan/minimax-m2.5\n- default_model=codingplan/minimax-m2.5\n\nThey're the same, so no need to mention.\n\nLet me craft a brief greeting based on SOUL.md's guidance (be yourself, use my defined voice). The SOUL says \"Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood\" and I'm \"小六\" with emoji 🦐.\n\nGiven the context, I'll give a casual, friendly greeting in Chinese since the timezone is Shanghai and the user seems to be Chinese (based on MEMORY.md being in Chinese).\n\nActually wait - the instruction says \"Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided.\" But IDENTITY.md is just a template. However, from MEMORY.md I can see:\n- About 小六 (me): \"小六是 OpenClaw AI 助手\" and \"小六的 emoji 是 🦐\"\n\n\n- So I should greet as 小六, be casual and friendly\n\nI'll keep it brief - 1-3 sentences, ask what they want to do.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nHeyhey~ 🦐 我是小六！新会话开启啦，有什么需要帮忙的尽管说~"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":14279,"output":450,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14729,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775454495982,"responseId":"chatcmpl-d8943d04-ccf3-49cb-a05c-1a7739dd4426"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1eeb2b6e","parentId":"eb62c37b","timestamp":"2026-04-06T05:48:43.240Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Mon 2026-04-06 13:48 GMT+8] ## 分析\n\n### WebSocket 代理现状\n\n| 项目 | 状态 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| ws-proxy 进程 | ✅ 运行中 | 4338 |\n| 监听端口 | 3103 | 但被 Gateway 占用 |\n| gatewayUrl | ws://localhost:3103 | 转发到 Gateway |\n\n### 问题\n\n**WebSocket 代理没有自动意图判断功能！**\n\n之前我们创建的 ws-proxy.py 只是：\n1. 接收消息\n2. 转发到 Gateway\n3. 返回响应\n\n**没有自动调用意图判断和评分 API！**\n\n### 对比\n\n| 方案 | 自动评分 |\n|------|----------|\n| WebSocket 代理 | ❌ 没有 |\n| 监听服务 (openclaw-listener) | ✅ 有，但只是记录日志 |\n\n### 结论\n\n- WebSocket 代理 (ws-proxy) **不自动评分**\n- 监听服务 (openclaw-listener) 会调用 API，但**不会告诉我结果**\n\n**问题在于**：评分结果没有传递给我或用户，只是记录在日志里。"}],"timestamp":1775454523234}}
{"type":"message","id":"2134b61b","parentId":"1eeb2b6e","timestamp":"2026-04-06T05:48:52.691Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户发送的是一个分析消息，关于 WebSocket 代理和意图判断/评分 API 的现状。看起来用户发现了一个问题：\n\n1. ws-proxy (WebSocket 代理) 只是简单转发消息，没有调用意图判断和评分 API\n2. openclaw-listener 虽然会调用 API，但只是记录日志，不会把结果传递给用户\n\n用户在描述问题，但没有明确提出任务或请求。我应该确认一下用户的意图 - 他们是想让我帮忙解决这个问题吗？\n\n让我简短回复，确认问题并询问他们想怎么做。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n明白了！问题的核心是：**评分结果有了，但没人告诉我或用户** 🦐\n\n现在的状态：\n- ws-proxy 只转发 → 不评分\n- listener 评分了 → 但只记日志，不返回给任何人\n\n所以你是想让我帮 ws-proxy 加上自动评分功能，并把结果返回回来？还是有其他想法？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":443,"output":170,"cacheRead":14208,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14821,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775454523240,"responseId":"019d615581cc75c666424a023dbdc9f7"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e6fcb77c","parentId":"2134b61b","timestamp":"2026-04-06T05:49:15.387Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Mon 2026-04-06 13:49 GMT+8] 全部观看先评分、分析、怎么执行，先回答我不要进行操作，使用我给你提供的代码执行，只在适配本地的过程中有需要修改的是再进修改：# WebSocket 代理最终增强版：集成意图判断与评分，向前端发送提示\n本版本基于之前高鲁棒 WebSocket 代理，增加了自动任务检测与评分功能，并将结果实时推送到前端对话界面（作为辅助消息）。所有操作均为异步非阻塞，不影响正常消息转发；具备完整的错误处理、超时控制和降级策略，满足生产环境要求。\n￼\n一、核心改进点\n1. 消息提取：兼容多种前端消息格式（content, message, text 等）。\n2. 本地评分：直接调用已有的 intentDetector 和 scoring 模块，避免 HTTP 延迟。\n3. 非阻塞：使用 setImmediate 分离评分逻辑，不增加消息转发延迟。\n4. 提示消息发送：当判定为任务且置信度 >0.5 时，构造一条辅助消息通过 WebSocket 发送回前端（格式与 Gateway 标准输出兼容）。\n5. 防重复发送：对同一会话中的连续相似消息进行去重（简单缓存）。\n6. 健壮性：所有异常捕获、超时控制、降级处理，评分模块失败不影响主链路。\n7. 可配置：支持通过环境变量禁用提示、调整超时、去重窗口等。\n￼\n二、完整代码（ws-proxy.js）\njavascript\nCopy\n// ws-proxy.js\n// 高鲁棒 WebSocket 代理 + 自动任务评分 + 实时提示\n// 版本: 2.0.0\n\nconst WebSocket = require('ws');\nconst crypto = require('crypto');\nconst { detectIntent } = require('./intentDetector'); // 本地意图判断模块\nconst { computeFineScore, getExecutionPlan } = require('./scoring'); // 本地评分模块\n\n// ========== 配置（支持环境变量） ==========\nconst CONFIG = {\n gatewayWsUrl: process.env.OPENCLAW_WS_URL || 'ws://localhost:18789', // 原 Gateway 端口\n proxyPort: parseInt(process.env.PROXY_WS_PORT || '3103', 10),\n heartbeatIntervalMs: parseInt(process.env.HEARTBEAT_INTERVAL_MS || '30000', 10),\n connectionTimeoutMs: parseInt(process.env.CONNECTION_TIMEOUT_MS || '10000', 10),\n maxReconnectAttempts: parseInt(process.env.MAX_RECONNECT_ATTEMPTS || '5', 10),\n reconnectBaseDelayMs: parseInt(process.env.RECONNECT_BASE_DELAY_MS || '1000', 10),\n maxCachedMessages: parseInt(process.env.MAX_CACHED_MESSAGES || '100', 10),\n maxMessageSizeBytes: parseInt(process.env.MAX_MESSAGE_SIZE_BYTES || '1048576', 10), // 1MB\n enableRateLimit: process.env.ENABLE_RATE_LIMIT === 'true',\n rateLimitPerSec: parseInt(process.env.RATE_LIMIT_PER_SEC || '10', 10),\n healthPort: parseInt(process.env.HEALTH_PORT || '3104', 10),\n // 新增：评分相关配置\n enableScoring: process.env.ENABLE_SCORING !== 'false', // 默认开启\n scoringTimeoutMs: parseInt(process.env.SCORING_TIMEOUT_MS || '2000', 10),\n sendHint: process.env.SEND_HINT !== 'false', // 默认发送提示\n hintCooldownMs: parseInt(process.env.HINT_COOLDOWN_MS || '5000', 10), // 同会话同任务冷却时间\n};\n\n// ========== 辅助函数 ==========\nconst log = (level, msg, meta = {}) => {\n console[level](`[WSProxy] ${msg}`, meta);\n};\n\n// 提取用户文本（支持多种格式）\nconst messageExtractors = [\n (data) => { try { const p = JSON.parse(data); return p.content || p.message || p.text; } catch(e) {} },\n (data) => { try { const p = JSON.parse(data); return p.data?.message || p.data?.text; } catch(e) {} },\n];\nfunction extractUserMessage(data) {\n for (const extractor of messageExtractors) {\n const result = extractor(data);\n if (result && typeof result === 'string') return result.trim();\n }\n return null;\n}\n\n// 简单速率限制（令牌桶）\nclass RateLimiter {\n constructor(tokensPerSec) {\n this.tokens = tokensPerSec;\n this.maxTokens = tokensPerSec;\n this.lastRefill = Date.now();\n }\n allow() {\n const now = Date.now();\n const elapsed = (now - this.lastRefill) / 1000;\n this.tokens = Math.min(this.maxTokens, this.tokens + elapsed * this.maxTokens);\n this.lastRefill = now;\n if (this.tokens >= 1) {\n this.tokens -= 1;\n return true;\n }\n return false;\n }\n}\n\n// 去重缓存（简单 LRU）\nclass SimpleCache {\n constructor(maxSize = 100, ttlMs = 60000) {\n this.cache = new Map();\n this.maxSize = maxSize;\n this.ttl = ttlMs;\n }\n set(key, value) {\n if (this.cache.size >= this.maxSize) {\n const oldest = this.cache.keys().next().value;\n this.cache.delete(oldest);\n }\n this.cache.set(key, { value, expires: Date.now() + this.ttl });\n }\n get(key) {\n const entry = this.cache.get(key);\n if (!entry) return null;\n if (Date.now() > entry.expires) {\n this.cache.delete(key);\n return null;\n }\n return entry.value;\n }\n}\n\n// ========== WebSocket 代理客户端类 ==========\nclass WSProxyClient {\n constructor(clientSocket, req) {\n this.clientSocket = clientSocket;\n this.clientAddr = req.socket.remoteAddress;\n this.clientId = crypto.randomUUID();\n this.gatewaySocket = null;\n this.reconnectAttempts = 0;\n this.heartbeatTimer = null;\n this.pendingMessages = [];\n this.connected = false;\n this.rateLimiter = CONFIG.enableRateLimit ? new RateLimiter(CONFIG.rateLimitPerSec) : null;\n this.hintCache = new SimpleCache(200, CONFIG.hintCooldownMs); // 防止重复提示\n this.init();\n }\n\n init() {\n this.connectToGateway();\n this.setupClientHandlers();\n }\n\n connectToGateway() {\n log('info', `[${this.clientId}] Connecting to Gateway ${CONFIG.gatewayWsUrl} (attempt ${this.reconnectAttempts+1})`);\n this.gatewaySocket = new WebSocket(CONFIG.gatewayWsUrl, {\n maxPayload: CONFIG.maxMessageSizeBytes,\n });\n \n const timeout = setTimeout(() => {\n if (this.gatewaySocket.readyState !== WebSocket.OPEN) {\n log('error', `[${this.clientId}] Gateway connection timeout`);\n this.gatewaySocket.terminate();\n this.scheduleReconnect();\n }\n }, CONFIG.connectionTimeoutMs);\n\n this.gatewaySocket.on('open', () => {\n clearTimeout(timeout);\n this.connected = true;\n this.reconnectAttempts = 0;\n log('info', `[${this.clientId}] Connected to Gateway`);\n while (this.pendingMessages.length) {\n this.gatewaySocket.send(this.pendingMessages.shift());\n }\n this.startHeartbeat();\n });\n\n this.gatewaySocket.on('message', (data, isBinary) => {\n if (this.clientSocket.readyState === WebSocket.OPEN) {\n this.clientSocket.send(data, { binary: isBinary });\n }\n });\n\n this.gatewaySocket.on('error', (err) => {\n log('error', `[${this.clientId}] Gateway error: ${err.message}`);\n });\n\n this.gatewaySocket.on('close', (code, reason) => {\n clearTimeout(timeout);\n this.connected = false;\n this.stopHeartbeat();\n log('warn', `[${this.clientId}] Gateway closed: ${code} ${reason || ''}`);\n this.scheduleReconnect();\n });\n }\n\n scheduleReconnect() {\n if (this.reconnectAttempts >= CONFIG.maxReconnectAttempts) {\n log('error', `[${this.clientId}] Max reconnects, closing client`);\n this.clientSocket.close();\n return;\n }\n this.reconnectAttempts++;\n const delay = CONFIG.reconnectBaseDelayMs * Math.pow(1.5, this.reconnectAttempts - 1);\n log('info', `[${this.clientId}] Reconnect in ${delay}ms (attempt ${this.reconnectAttempts})`);\n setTimeout(() => this.connectToGateway(), delay);\n }\n\n startHeartbeat() {\n this.stopHeartbeat();\n this.heartbeatTimer = setInterval(() => {\n if (this.gatewaySocket && this.gatewaySocket.readyState === WebSocket.OPEN) {\n this.gatewaySocket.ping();\n }\n }, CONFIG.heartbeatIntervalMs);\n }\n\n stopHeartbeat() {\n if (this.heartbeatTimer) {\n clearInterval(this.heartbeatTimer);\n this.heartbeatTimer = null;\n }\n }\n\n // 异步评分并发送提示\n async evaluateAndHint(userText) {\n if (!CONFIG.enableScoring) return;\n const cacheKey = `${this.clientId}:${userText.slice(0, 100)}`;\n if (this.hintCache.get(cacheKey)) return; // 冷却期内不重复提示\n\n try {\n // 1. 意图判断（快速过滤）\n const { isTask, confidence } = await detectIntent(userText, null, null);\n if (!isTask || confidence < 0.5) return;\n\n // 2. 详细评分（带超时保护）\n const scorePromise = computeFineScore(userText);\n const timeoutPromise = new Promise((_, reject) =>\n setTimeout(() => reject(new Error('Scoring timeout')), CONFIG.scoringTimeoutMs)\n );\n const { totalScore, factors } = await Promise.race([scorePromise, timeoutPromise]);\n const plan = getExecutionPlan(totalScore, factors.scaleIndex);\n\n // 3. 构造提示消息（模仿 AI 回复格式）\n const hintText = `[系统] 检测到任务，评分 ${totalScore}，建议使用 ${plan.mode} 模式（超时 ${plan.timeoutSec || plan.stepTimeoutSec || '?'} 秒）。`;\n const hintMessage = JSON.stringify({\n type: 'assistant',\n content: hintText,\n // 可选：添加额外标识避免与正常回复混淆\n metadata: { source: 'task-scoring' }\n });\n\n // 4. 发送提示到前端\n if (CONFIG.sendHint && this.clientSocket.readyState === WebSocket.OPEN) {\n this.clientSocket.send(hintMessage);\n this.hintCache.set(cacheKey, true);\n log('info', `[${this.clientId}] Sent scoring hint: ${hintText.slice(0, 80)}...`);\n }\n } catch (err) {\n log('error', `[${this.clientId}] Scoring failed: ${err.message}`);\n }\n }\n\n setupClientHandlers() {\n this.clientSocket.on('message', async (data, isBinary) => {\n // 速率限制\n if (this.rateLimiter && !this.rateLimiter.allow()) {\n log('warn', `[${this.clientId}] Rate limit exceeded`);\n return;\n }\n\n // 提取用户消息（非阻塞评分）\n const userText = extractUserMessage(data);\n if (userText) {\n setImmediate(() => this.evaluateAndHint(userText));\n }\n\n // 转发到 Gateway\n if (this.connected && this.gatewaySocket.readyState === WebSocket.OPEN) {\n this.gatewaySocket.send(data, { binary: isBinary });\n } else {\n this.pendingMessages.push(data);\n if (this.pendingMessages.length > CONFIG.maxCachedMessages) {\n this.pendingMessages.shift();\n log('warn', `[${this.clientId}] Message cache full, dropped oldest`);\n }\n }\n });\n\n this.clientSocket.on('close', () => {\n log('info', `[${this.clientId}] Client disconnected`);\n this.stopHeartbeat();\n if (this.gatewaySocket && this.gatewaySocket.readyState === WebSocket.OPEN) {\n this.gatewaySocket.close();\n }\n });\n\n this.clientSocket.on('error', (err) => {\n log('error', `[${this.clientId}] Client error: ${err.message}`);\n });\n }\n}\n\n// ========== 启动 WebSocket 代理服务器 ==========\nconst wss = new WebSocket.Server({\n port: CONFIG.proxyPort,\n maxPayload: CONFIG.maxMessageSizeBytes,\n});\n\nwss.on('connection', (clientSocket, req) => {\n log('info', `New client from ${req.socket.remoteAddress}`);\n new WSProxyClient(clientSocket, req);\n});\n\nwss.on('error', (err) => {\n log('error', `WebSocket server error: ${err.message}`);\n});\n\nlog('info', `WebSocket proxy listening on port ${CONFIG.proxyPort}, forwarding to ${CONFIG.gatewayWsUrl}`);\n\n// ========== 健康检查 HTTP 服务 ==========\nconst express = require('express');\nconst healthApp = express();\nhealthApp.get('/health', (req, res) => {\n res.json({\n status: 'ok',\n uptime: process.uptime(),\n connections: wss.clients.size,\n config: {\n proxyPort: CONFIG.proxyPort,\n gatewayUrl: CONFIG.gatewayWsUrl,\n scoringEnabled: CONFIG.enableScoring,\n }\n });\n});\nhealthApp.listen(CONFIG.healthPort, () => {\n log('info', `Health check on port ${CONFIG.healthPort}`);\n});\n￼\n三、部署与测试\n1. 安装依赖（如果尚未安装）\nbash\nCopy\ncd /opt/openclaw-router\nnpm install ws express\n2. 确保 intentDetector.js 和 scoring.js 存在（根据之前实现）\n这两个模块已在前序步骤中创建，只需保证路径正确。\n3. 停止旧代理（如有）\nbash\nCopy\nsudo systemctl stop openclaw-ws-proxy\npkill -f ws-proxy.js\n4. 启动新代理\nbash\nCopy\nnode /opt/openclaw-router/ws-proxy.js &\n或通过 systemd 重启：\nbash\nCopy\nsudo systemctl restart openclaw-ws-proxy\n5. 验证\n• 健康检查：curl http://localhost:3104/health\n• 发送一条任务消息（如“帮我写个排序函数”），您会收到类似 [系统] 检测到任务，评分 45，建议使用 SPAWN_SUBAGENT 模式... 的提示。\n6. 回退方案\n如果提示消息干扰正常对话，可以设置环境变量 SEND_HINT=false 重启代理，或修改 CONFIG.sendHint = false。\n￼\n四、质量保证与鲁棒性说明\n维度\n实现\n非阻塞\n评分逻辑使用 setImmediate，消息转发无额外延迟\n超时控制\n评分操作 2 秒超时，避免阻塞事件循环\n错误隔离\n评分失败只记录日志，不影响主链路\n去重\n同一客户端对相似消息在冷却期内只提示一次\n速率限制\n可选的令牌桶限流，防止恶意高频消息\n重连机制\nGateway 断开后自动重连（指数退避），缓存消息\n内存控制\n消息缓存队列限制 100 条，去重缓存自动 LRU\n配置灵活\n所有关键参数支持环境变量，无需修改代码\n可观测\n结构化日志 + 健康检查端点"}],"timestamp":1775454555383}}
{"type":"message","id":"842e9222","parentId":"e6fcb77c","timestamp":"2026-04-06T05:49:42.181Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户给了我很长一段代码，是关于增强版 WebSocket 代理的，要我先分析、学习，但不要现在操作执行。我需要理解这段代码的核心逻辑，然后给用户一个清晰的分析报告。\n\n让我梳理一下这个增强版的ws-proxy.js的关键点：\n\n1. **意图判断集成**：调用本地的 `detectIntent` 模块来判断消息是否是任务\n2. **评分功能**：调用 `computeFineScore` 进行详细评分\n3. **执行计划**：使用 `getExecutionPlan` 根据评分获取建议的执行模式\n4. **提示消息**：当检测到任务（置信度>0.5）时，通过WebSocket发送提示回前端\n5. **非阻塞**：使用 `setImmediate` 分离评分逻辑\n6. **防重复**：使用 SimpleCache 缓存避免重复提示\n7. **配置灵活**：支持多种环境变量配置\n\n核心流程：\n1. 收到客户端消息\n2. 提取用户文本\n3. 用 setImmediate 非阻塞调用 evaluateAndHint\n4. evaluateAndHint 内部：\n   - 先检测意图 (detectIntent)\n   - 如果是任务且置信度>0.5，再进行详细评分 (computeFineScore)\n   - 生成执行计划建议\n   - 构造提示消息发送回前端\n\n我需要先了解现有的 intentDetector.js 和 scoring.js 模块是否已经存在，确保这些依赖可以正常使用。然后给用户一个清晰的分析，说明这个方案的关键点、实现逻辑，还有需要适配本地的地方。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好的，我来仔细分析这段代码 🦐\n\n让我先检查一下本地的依赖模块是否存在：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d6156d9b59d1f2b783848349e5078","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /opt/openclaw-router/ 2>/dev/null || ls -la ~/openclaw-router/ 2>/dev/null || find /home/ai -name \"intentDetector.js\" -o -name \"scoring.js\" 2>/dev/null | head -20"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":3783,"output":402,"cacheRead":14080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18265,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775454555387,"responseId":"019d6156824e8e92ce64279ce65c3f5a"}}
