{"type":"message","id":"f71656a8","parentId":"08c8198c","timestamp":"2026-04-06T06:03:52.473Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the issue! The health endpoint shows:\n- `gatewayUrl: \"ws://localhost:3103\"` - This is wrong! It should be `ws://localhost:18789` (the Gateway port)\n\nBut wait, this means the ws-proxy.js is running and has a health endpoint at port 3104. But the user said the scoring results aren't being sent to the frontend. Let me check if the current ws-proxy.js has the scoring feature or not.\n\nLet me read the current ws-proxy.js to see if it has scoring functionality.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7bbb8170dea0430882d86373","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"head -50 ~/openclaw-router/ws-proxy.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":23641,"output":147,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23788,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775455430011,"responseId":"chatcmpl-4bc86fbd-6bc5-408e-a8d6-49899042af14"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a67321a0","parentId":"f71656a8","timestamp":"2026-04-06T06:03:52.502Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_7bbb8170dea0430882d86373","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// ws-proxy.js\n// 高鲁棒 WebSocket 代理，集成意图判断与任务评分\n\nconst WebSocket = require('ws');\nconst crypto = require('crypto');\nconst { detectIntent } = require('./intentDetector');\nconst { computeFineScore, getExecutionPlan } = require('./scoring');\n\nconst CONFIG = {\n gatewayWsUrl: process.env.OPENCLAW_WS_URL || 'ws://localhost:3103',\n proxyPort: parseInt(process.env.PROXY_WS_PORT || '3103', 10),\n heartbeatIntervalMs: parseInt(process.env.HEARTBEAT_INTERVAL_MS || '30000', 10),\n connectionTimeoutMs: parseInt(process.env.CONNECTION_TIMEOUT_MS || '10000', 10),\n maxReconnectAttempts: parseInt(process.env.MAX_RECONNECT_ATTEMPTS || '5', 10),\n reconnectBaseDelayMs: parseInt(process.env.RECONNECT_BASE_DELAY_MS || '1000', 10),\n maxCachedMessages: parseInt(process.env.MAX_CACHED_MESSAGES || '100', 10),\n maxMessageSizeBytes: parseInt(process.env.MAX_MESSAGE_SIZE_BYTES || '1048576', 10),\n enableRateLimit: process.env.ENABLE_RATE_LIMIT === 'true',\n rateLimitPerSec: parseInt(process.env.RATE_LIMIT_PER_SEC || '10', 10),\n healthPort: parseInt(process.env.HEALTH_PORT || '3104', 10),\n};\n\nconst log = (level, msg, meta = {}) => {\n console[level](`[WSProxy] ${msg}`, JSON.stringify(meta));\n};\n\nconst messageExtractors = [\n (data) => { try { const p = JSON.parse(data); return p.content || p.message || p.text; } catch(e) {} },\n (data) => { try { const p = JSON.parse(data); return p.data?.message || p.data?.text; } catch(e) {} },\n];\n\nfunction extractUserMessage(data) {\n for (const extractor of messageExtractors) {\n const result = extractor(data);\n if (result && typeof result === 'string') return result;\n }\n return null;\n}\n\nclass RateLimiter {\n constructor(tokensPerSec) {\n this.tokens = tokensPerSec;\n this.maxTokens = tokensPerSec;\n this.lastRefill = Date.now();\n }\n allow() {\n const now = Date.now();\n const elapsed = (now - this.lastRefill) / 1000;\n this.tokens = Math.min(this.maxTokens, this.tokens + elapsed * this.maxTokens);\n this.lastRefill = now;"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":13,"aggregated":"// ws-proxy.js\n// 高鲁棒 WebSocket 代理，集成意图判断与任务评分\n\nconst WebSocket = require('ws');\nconst crypto = require('crypto');\nconst { detectIntent } = require('./intentDetector');\nconst { computeFineScore, getExecutionPlan } = require('./scoring');\n\nconst CONFIG = {\n gatewayWsUrl: process.env.OPENCLAW_WS_URL || 'ws://localhost:3103',\n proxyPort: parseInt(process.env.PROXY_WS_PORT || '3103', 10),\n heartbeatIntervalMs: parseInt(process.env.HEARTBEAT_INTERVAL_MS || '30000', 10),\n connectionTimeoutMs: parseInt(process.env.CONNECTION_TIMEOUT_MS || '10000', 10),\n maxReconnectAttempts: parseInt(process.env.MAX_RECONNECT_ATTEMPTS || '5', 10),\n reconnectBaseDelayMs: parseInt(process.env.RECONNECT_BASE_DELAY_MS || '1000', 10),\n maxCachedMessages: parseInt(process.env.MAX_CACHED_MESSAGES || '100', 10),\n maxMessageSizeBytes: parseInt(process.env.MAX_MESSAGE_SIZE_BYTES || '1048576', 10),\n enableRateLimit: process.env.ENABLE_RATE_LIMIT === 'true',\n rateLimitPerSec: parseInt(process.env.RATE_LIMIT_PER_SEC || '10', 10),\n healthPort: parseInt(process.env.HEALTH_PORT || '3104', 10),\n};\n\nconst log = (level, msg, meta = {}) => {\n console[level](`[WSProxy] ${msg}`, JSON.stringify(meta));\n};\n\nconst messageExtractors = [\n (data) => { try { const p = JSON.parse(data); return p.content || p.message || p.text; } catch(e) {} },\n (data) => { try { const p = JSON.parse(data); return p.data?.message || p.data?.text; } catch(e) {} },\n];\n\nfunction extractUserMessage(data) {\n for (const extractor of messageExtractors) {\n const result = extractor(data);\n if (result && typeof result === 'string') return result;\n }\n return null;\n}\n\nclass RateLimiter {\n constructor(tokensPerSec) {\n this.tokens = tokensPerSec;\n this.maxTokens = tokensPerSec;\n this.lastRefill = Date.now();\n }\n allow() {\n const now = Date.now();\n const elapsed = (now - this.lastRefill) / 1000;\n this.tokens = Math.min(this.maxTokens, this.tokens + elapsed * this.maxTokens);\n this.lastRefill = now;","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775455432496}}
{"type":"message","id":"a47110e9","parentId":"a67321a0","timestamp":"2026-04-06T06:04:09.877Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see! The current ws-proxy.js already has the scoring functionality (it imports `detectIntent` and `computeFineScore`, `getExecutionPlan`). So the scoring code is already there.\n\nBut wait, the user's question \"怎么回事\" might be asking what happened after they said \"执行\" (execute). I realize I didn't actually DO anything - I just scored the task but didn't execute it.\n\nWait, let me re-read the conversation:\n1. User sent the code for the enhanced ws-proxy\n2. I analyzed it\n3. User said \"评分一下\"\n4. I scored it (75/100)\n5. User said \"进行任务评分\"\n6. I scored the deployment task (47/100, SPAWN_SUBAGENT mode)\n7. User said \"执行\"\n8. Then at 14:03 user said \"怎么回事\"\n\nSo the user said \"执行\" (execute) and I didn't actually execute anything! I think they want to know why the deployment didn't happen.\n\nLet me now actually execute the deployment. The task score is 47, which means SPAWN_SUBAGENT is recommended. But it's simpler to just do it directly since it's just:\n1. Backup current ws-proxy.js\n2. Write new one \n3. Restart the service\n\nLet me do this now.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n抱歉！我理解了一—你说\"执行\"后我没实际动手，只顾着评分了 😂\n\n现在马上部署增强版 ws-proxy！\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d61639cf3bb70fb4e0e31788ebf52","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cp ~/openclaw-router/ws-proxy.js ~/openclaw-router/ws-proxy.js.bak.$(date +%Y%m%d%H%M%S)"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":10308,"output":351,"cacheRead":14080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24739,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775455432502,"responseId":"019d61636143f2751dfc96719d940ddd"}}
