{"type":"message","id":"b99694db","parentId":"d83ca326","timestamp":"2026-04-06T07:40:28.255Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看到了！Gateway 配置在 3103 端口：`\"gateway\": { \"port\": 3103, ...}`\n\n而 ws-proxy 在 3107 端口。\n\n问题很可能是：\n1. 前端通过 Gateway (3103) 连接，没有经过 ws-proxy (3103)\n2. 所以评分逻辑根本就没触发\n\n解决方案有两个：\n1. 修改 Gateway 配置，让前端通过 ws-proxy (3107) 连接\n2. 或者把 ws-proxy 改回 3103，让 Gateway 换个端口\n\n让我确认一下 controlUI 绑定的端口。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f907f88b29fb40e48d6e7bd1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 看看控制界面怎么连接的\nss -tlnp | grep -E \"node|openclaw\" | grep LISTEN"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":45370,"output":165,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45535,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775461224362,"responseId":"chatcmpl-def6dbf0-4c2d-4fa3-afeb-6560070a28f3"}}
