{"type":"message","id":"e080d4e7","parentId":"91314de6","timestamp":"2026-04-06T07:40:42.626Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在清楚了：\n- 3103 = Gateway (ws)\n- 3104 = ws-proxy 健康检查\n- 3105 = Gateway 某个额外端口\n- 3107 = ws-proxy (我们的评分代理)\n\n前端直接连 3103(Gateway)，没经过 3107(ws-proxy)，所以评分没触发。\n\n**解决方案**：让前端连 3107 而不是 3103。但这可能需要修改前端配置或者让 Gateway 把 WebSocket 请求代理到我们的 ws-proxy。\n\n更简单的方案是：把 ws-proxy 改成 Gateway 的一部分，让 Gateway 内置评分功能。但这需要改 Gateway 代码。\n\n另一个方案是：让 Gateway 把 WebSocket 请求转发到 3107。但 Gateway 可能不支持这种代理。\n\n让我问用户他前端是怎么配置的，或者看看 control-ui 怎么连接。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d61bbcd7108926dd2fb6b94982b21","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查 control-ui 配置\ncat ~/.openclaw/config.yaml 2>/dev/null || echo \"no yaml\"\ngrep -r \"3107\\|control\" ~/.openclaw/extensions/ 2>/dev/null | head -5"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":45613,"output":232,"cacheRead":256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46101,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775461228290,"responseId":"019d61bb9e5b77ac2e211d8bae4cab4d"}}
