{"type":"message","id":"0850f94a","parentId":"a4c7297a","timestamp":"2026-04-06T07:41:04.300Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我直接看问题：Gateway 监听 3103，前端连 3103。我们的 ws-proxy 在 3107，但前端没连那里。\n\n解决方案：\n1. 让 ws-proxy 成为 Gateway 的上游代理\n2. 或者让 Gateway 把 WebSocket 请求转发到 ws-proxy\n\n更实际的解决方案：把 ws-proxy 改成 3103，然后让 Gateway 用其他端口。但这样 Gateway 也要改。\n\n最简单的方案：检查 Gateway 的 WebSocket 配置，看能不能把流量先走到 ws-proxy (3107)。\n\n让我看看 Gateway 代码有没有 WebSocket 代理功能。或者我们可以让前端改连 3107。这需要用户提供他前端的配置信息。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n问题找到了：\n\n| 端口 | 进程 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 3103 | Gateway | 你前端现在连这里 |\n| 3107 | ws-proxy (评分) | 前端没连 |\n\n**你前端连的是 `ws://localhost:3103`**，没有经过 ws-proxy，所以评分没触发。\n\n**两个解决方案**：\n\n1. **改前端配置** → 连 `ws://localhost:3107`（需要你能改前端配置）\n2. **改 ws-proxy 端口** → 让 ws-proxy 在 3103，把 Gateway 搬到其他端口\n\n你那边能改前端 WebSocket 地址吗？🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":474,"output":269,"cacheRead":45824,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46567,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775461248906,"responseId":"019d61bca4563b45867a776bb55b2c7a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"71862a62","parentId":"0850f94a","timestamp":"2026-04-06T07:43:44.723Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Mon 2026-04-06 15:43 GMT+8] 改前端配置 ，告诉我你要怎么改"}],"timestamp":1775461424717}}
{"type":"message","id":"6d7398c8","parentId":"71862a62","timestamp":"2026-04-06T07:43:58.012Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户同意改前端配置，需要告诉他怎么改。但我需要先找到前端配置在哪里。前端配置可能在哪里呢？\n\n1. 可能是通过 controlUi 插件加载的\n2. 可能是 Gateway 自带的 control UI\n\n看到配置里有 `\"controlUi\": { \"allowInsecureAuth\": true, \"enabled\": true }`，这说明 Gateway 自带了一个控制界面。\n\n让我检查一下这个控制界面怎么配置 WebSocket 地址的。也许需要修改 Gateway 的启动参数或环境变量。\n\n另一个可能是 ws-proxy 需要在 Gateway 前面做反向代理，而不是客户端直连。\n\n其实最简单的方法是：让 ws-proxy 监听 3103 端口（替换 Gateway），然后让 Gateway 用别的端口。但这需要修改 Gateway 配置，可能更复杂。\n\n让我先检查一下 Gateway 的环境变量或者启动配置，看看 WebSocket 端口能不能改。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d61bf7e8aa1c69beca55db5e79ad5","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 查看 Gateway 怎么启动的\nsystemctl show openclaw-gateway --no-pager | grep -E \"ExecStart|Environment\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":2633,"output":222,"cacheRead":43520,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46375,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775461424722,"responseId":"019d61bf51e342d7e48c916d3793d6b5"}}
