{"type":"message","id":"637123f8","parentId":"dd6610c9","timestamp":"2026-04-06T07:44:35.114Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Gateway 是单文件进程，配置来自 openclaw.json 里的 `\"gateway\": { \"port\": 3103 }`。\n\n最简单的方法是：\n1. 改 openclaw.json 里的 gateway.port 为其他端口（比如 3108）\n2. 重启 Gateway\n3. 然后把 ws-proxy 改成 3103\n\n或者更简单的方法：告诉用户怎么在前端改配置。但我需要先知道前端连的是哪个地址。\n\n实际上，更简单的方案是：让 ws-proxy 作为 Gateway 的上游代理，客户端还是连 3103，但 3103 端口先到 ws-proxy，ws-proxy 再转发给 Gateway。\n\n等等，现在的状态是：\n- Gateway 监听 3103- ws-proxy 监听 3107 → 转发到 3103\n\n如果我把 ws-proxy 改成监听 3103，转发到 3105（需要把 Gateway 移到 3105）……\n\n或者最简单的：直接让用户改前端连接地址为 3107。但用户说他不知道前端怎么配置的。\n\n让我看看有没有 control-ui 的配置，或者 Gateway 带的 UI 哪里设置地址的\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d61c00efb3fd5345a523520103d1a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 查看 Gateway 自带的 controlUI 配置\n# 在 openclaw.json 里 gateway.controlUi\ngrep -A5 \"controlUi\" ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":168,"output":281,"cacheRead":46464,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46913,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775461451669,"responseId":"019d61bfbd3ab49294b95404991b84e7"}}
