{"type":"message","id":"67f3119c","parentId":"afc11e08","timestamp":"2026-04-06T07:44:52.338Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"JS 文件被打包了。让我看看有没有其他方式配置。最简单的方案还是改端口。让我给用户一个最简单的方案：\n1. 改 openclaw.json 里的 gateway.port 从 3103 改成 31082. 重启 Gateway\n3. 改 ws-proxy 的 gatewayWsUrl 从 3103 改成 31084. 重启 ws-proxy\n5. ws-proxy 现在监听 3103\n\n这样前端不用改任何配置，还是连 3103，但会先经过 ws-proxy（评分）。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n最简单的方案是**调换端口**，让 ws-proxy 占领 3103：\n\n**步骤：**\n\n1. **改 Gateway 端口 → 3108**\n```bash\n# 编辑配置\nnano ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n```\n找到 `\"gateway\": { \"port\": 3103` 改成 `\"port\": 3108`\n\n2. **重启 Gateway**\n```bash\n# 先杀掉旧进程\npkill openclaw-gateway\n# 启动新的\nopenclaw gateway start\n```\n\n3. **改 ws-proxy 转发目标 → 3108**\n```bash\n# 修改 ws-proxy.js 配置\n# 把 gatewayWsUrl 从 3103 改成 3108\n```\n\n要我帮你改吗？🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":47579,"output":259,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47838,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775461489740,"responseId":"chatcmpl-fc14a309-1fc8-4119-9a88-21c345b25db8"}}
