{"type":"message","id":"48c3e5ae","parentId":"16b296f0","timestamp":"2026-04-06T08:03:13.246Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到了！Gateway 一直断开连接（1000 close）。这可能是因为 Gateway 没有接受 ws-proxy 的连接认证。\n\n让我检查评分代码是否正确执行，以及问题是否在于 Gateway 认证。让我先手动测试评分是否能正常推送提示到客户端。但我没有用户那边的连接...\n\n让我检查一下评分代码中的逻辑是否有问题。让我看看evaluateAndHint函数是否被调用了。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d61d05c6954ab84571f30399ce02d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 直接用 WebSocket client 测试\ncd ~/openclaw-router && node -e \"\nconst WebSocket = require('ws');\nconst ws = new WebSocket('ws://localhost:3103');\n\nws.on('open', () => {\n  console.log('Connected!');\n  ws.send(JSON.stringify({content: '测试评分功能'}));\n});\n\nws.on('message', (data) => {\n  const msg = data.toString();\n  console.log('收到:', msg.slice(0, 100));\n});\n\nsetTimeout(() => ws.close(), 5000);\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":1583,"output":214,"cacheRead":54400,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56197,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775462574534,"responseId":"019d61d02c496f2cf6c7ca52820f7750"}}
