{"type":"message","id":"2ad85ddc","parentId":"0defdf65","timestamp":"2026-04-06T08:05:26.713Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户在问我是不是傻...可能他们遇到了什么问题。让我想想可能的问题：\n\n1. 评分功能实际上没有推送到前端 - 我测试是能收到的，但用户说没有\n2. 可能是消息格式问题 - 前端没有正确显示 system 类型的消息\n\n让我直接检查一下 ws-proxy 的代码，看看提示消息是怎么发送的...问题可能是评分成功但消息没发到客户端？或者发到了但前端没显示？\n\n让我仔细看看 ws-proxy.js 中 evaluateAndHint 函数的逻辑。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_873f972bc4bd4e339e90445f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查评分提示是否真的发送到客户端\ncd ~/openclaw-router && node -e \"\nconst WebSocket = require('ws');\nconst ws = new WebSocket('ws://localhost:3103');\n\nlet gotScoreHint = false;\n\nws.on('open', () => {\n  ws.send(JSON.stringify({content: '用 Python 写一个冒泡排序算法'}));\n});\n\nws.on('message', (data) => {\n  const msg = JSON.parse(data.toString());\n  if (msg.type === 'system' && msg.metadata?.source === 'task-scoring') {\n    console.log('✅ 评分提示已发送:', msg.content);\n    gotScoreHint = true;\n  }\n});\n\nsetTimeout(() => {\n  console.log(gotScoreHint ? '测试通过' : '没收到提示');\n  ws.close();\n}, 5000);\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":57200,"output":300,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57500,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775462721586,"responseId":"chatcmpl-a1c11007-8ea9-440e-89d1-40e45cc02937"}}
