{"type":"message","id":"d790bd27","parentId":"f4cbf2db","timestamp":"2026-04-06T08:16:56.651Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"还是立即断开。添加 token 也没解决问题。可能 Gateway 确实在拒绝非前端连接，或者代码本身可能有某种保护机制阻止来自非认证来源的连接。让我想想其他方法。可能的问题是：1. Gateway 可能有来源 IP 限制\n2. 或者需要特定的消息格式\n3. 或者需要某种握手\n\n让我尝试另一种方法：既然前端可以正常工作，我们可以让前端发送消息时带上评分信息，而不是让 ws-proxy 代理服务器自己去做。\n\n或者，也许问题是 ws-proxy 作为 \"客户端连接到 Gateway\" 时，Gateway 把它当作一个需要认证的前端，但 ws-proxy 没有完成认证流程（没有响应 challenge）。让我看看 Gateway 代码有什么要求。但实际上，如果前端可以工作，说明 Gateway 确实需要某些认证。让我再仔细想想这个问题。\n\n实际上，我注意到一个问题：当 Gateway 发送 connect.challenge 时，它期望客户端响应这个 challenge。ws-proxy 可能需要响应这个 challenge 才能保持连接。但目前的代码没有处理 challenge 的逻辑。\n\n让我添加处理 challenge 的代码，让 ws-proxy 能够响应 Gateway 的认证挑战。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n还是被关。Gateway 和 ws-proxy 之间需要完成认证 handshake！\n\n让我加 上 challenge 响应：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d61ddae4467532d16d937bc27563c","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":120,"path":"/home/ai/openclaw-router/ws-proxy.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":1551,"output":282,"cacheRead":69504,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71337,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775463391953,"responseId":"019d61dd5a161d422b7a778ca32e9490"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e03f9048","parentId":"d790bd27","timestamp":"2026-04-06T08:16:56.681Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d61ddae4467532d16d937bc27563c","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":" }\n });\n \n const timeout = setTimeout(() => {\n if (this.gatewaySocket.readyState !== WebSocket.OPEN) {\n log('error', `[${this.clientId}] Gateway connection timeout`);\n this.gatewaySocket.terminate();\n this.scheduleReconnect();\n }\n }, CONFIG.connectionTimeoutMs);\n\n this.gatewaySocket.on('open', () => {\n clearTimeout(timeout);\n this.connected = true;\n this.reconnectAttempts = 0;\n log('info', `[${this.clientId}] Connected to Gateway`);\n while (this.pendingMessages.length) {\n this.gatewaySocket.send(this.pendingMessages.shift());\n }\n this.startHeartbeat();\n });\n\n this.gatewaySocket.on('message', (data, isBinary) => {\n if (this.clientSocket.readyState === WebSocket.OPEN) {\n // 附加评分提示到 AI 响应\n const scoredData = this.appendScoreHint(data);\n this.clientSocket.send(scoredData, { binary: isBinary });\n }\n });\n\n\n[158 more lines in file. Use offset=150 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775463416672}}
{"type":"message","id":"70945923","parentId":"e03f9048","timestamp":"2026-04-06T08:17:21.523Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我需要在收到 message 时处理 connect.challenge 事件。让我添加处理 challenge 的逻辑。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d61ddcebb8483449e1554ebf5cd74","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":" this.gatewaySocket.on('message', (data, isBinary) => {\n try {\n const msg = JSON.parse(data.toString());\n // 处理认证挑战\n if (msg.type === 'event' && msg.event === 'connect.challenge') {\n const nonce = msg.payload?.nonce;\n if (nonce) {\n // 生成响应\n const response = JSON.stringify({\n type: 'response',\n event: 'connect.challenge',\n payload: { nonce, response: nonce }\n });\n this.gatewaySocket.send(response);\n log('info', `[${this.clientId}] Sent challenge response`);\n return;\n }\n }\n } catch(e) {}\n \n if (this.clientSocket.readyState === WebSocket.OPEN) {\n // 附加评分提示到 AI 响应\n const scoredData = this.appendScoreHint(data);\n this.clientSocket.send(scoredData, { binary: isBinary });\n }\n });","oldText":" this.gatewaySocket.on('message', (data, isBinary) => {\n if (this.clientSocket.readyState === WebSocket.OPEN) {\n // 附加评分提示到 AI 响应\n const scoredData = this.appendScoreHint(data);\n this.clientSocket.send(scoredData, { binary: isBinary });\n }\n });"}],"path":"/home/ai/openclaw-router/ws-proxy.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":1419,"output":350,"cacheRead":70144,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71913,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775463416682,"responseId":"019d61ddc0b212634d7e01f3c47e8a5f"}}
