{"type":"message","id":"46f2fdaa","parentId":"9a71e284","timestamp":"2026-04-06T08:31:34.796Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"评分 API 工作正常！CORS 也加上了 ✅\n\n现在前端可以通过 HTTP 调用评分：\n- URL: `http://localhost:3102/api/score?task=消息内容`\n- 或者 POST: `http://localhost:3102/api/task` with JSON `{\"taskSpec\": \"消息内容\"}`\n\nAPI 添加了 CORS 支持，前端可以直接调用了 ✅\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n✅ 好了！评分 API 已添加 CORS 支持：\n\n**调用方式**：\n```bash\n# GET\ncurl \"http://localhost:3102/api/score?task=用Python写一个冒泡排序\"\n\n# POST\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:3102/api/task \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"taskSpec\": \"用Python写一个冒泡排序\"}'\n```\n\n**响应示例**：\n```json\n{\n  \"score\": { \"totalScore\": 20, \"factors\": {...} },\n  \"plan\": { \"mode\": \"DIRECT\", \"timeoutSec\": 30 }\n}\n```\n\n现在前端可以直接调用这个 API 显示评分了 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":76626,"output":228,"cacheRead":256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77110,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775464276125,"responseId":"019d61ea3acdd6853002cc3803644d91"}}
